layout: default
title: "Investuj do sebe a přijď na školení"
id: vzdelavej-se

open_form_link: "https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf-x6HlwpfIB-Ig_oyrPzk7PKbyF4YMIHLH21n_dV9V5Edmyw/viewform"
